```purs
import Prelude
import Effect
import Effect.Console

foo :: Int -> Effect Int
foo x =
  let
      two = one + 1
   in do
      log "asdf"
      let asdf = log "asdf"
      asdf
      pure two
  where
  one = 1 + 1

  dothmth = do
     log "qwe"
     log "qwe1"
```
